@page "/daisyui"
<PageTitle>Tailwind / DaisyUI - Saascade Docs</PageTitle>

<h1>Tailwind / DaisyUI</h1>

<main class="documentation">

    <section class="card">

        <h2>Overview</h2>

        <p class="subtitle">
            DaisyUI is a Tailwind CSS component plugin that provides semantic class names
            like <code>card</code>, <code>btn</code>, and <code>hero</code>.
        </p>

        <hr />

        <h3>Setup</h3>

        <pre><code>builder.Services.AddSingleton&lt;IDesignSystem&gt;(DesignSystems.Tailwind.DaisyUI);</code></pre>

    </section>

    <section class="card">

        <h2>Specializations</h2>

        <p>
            DaisyUI components support specializations such as <code>bg-base-100</code>,
            <code>w-96</code>, <code>shadow-sm</code>, which are returned by
            <code>GetSpecializations()</code>.
        </p>

    </section>

</main>
